text: Milica Kostić (born 21 December 1997) is a Serbian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper and has appeared for the Serbia women's national team. ==Career== Kostić has been capped for the Serbia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Serbian women's footballers Category:Serbia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:ŽFK Spartak Subotica players
